  voxtral.c is a from-scratch C implementation of Mistral's Voxtral
  speech-to-text model and is the on-device transcription engine used
  by OpenDictation. The vendored copy in app/Vendor/voxtral/ contains
  local modifications for macOS microphone capture and Metal kernel
  integration. See app/Vendor/voxtral/LICENSE.upstream for the full
  upstream MIT License and copyright notice, and
  app/Vendor/voxtral/README.md for a description of local changes.
